e contemporain, d’un travail nécessaire sur soi et pour soi…   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aIdentity (Psychology) in adolescence. 0aSelfies (Photography)xPsychological aspects. 0aSelfies (Photography)xSocial aspects. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / General.2bisacsh1 aFontcuberta, Joan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLachance, Jocelyn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLeroux, Yann, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aLeroux, Yann, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLimare, Sophie, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aLimare, Sophie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311127365508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2017z978311127619940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978276373325840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763733258423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763733258/original  a978-3-11-127365-5  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-127619-9  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles